           SHORT="GKrellM plugin which monitors the CapsLock, NumLock and"
cat << EOF
gkleds is a GKrellM plugin which monitors the CapsLock, NumLock and ScrollLock
keys and reports their current status via on screen LEDs.  This is useful
for people who have keyboards without LEDs, typically cordless keyboards.
It also lets you toggle the indicator state via mouse clicks.
EOF
